  "texts": [
    "When different SMILES tokens played a similar role in the molecule such as 'c1ccccc1)' and 'c1ccccc1' in the molecule 7, their attention patterns were similar as well.",
    "This result demonstrated that SPMM could capture the relations between molecule structures and chemical properties without explicitly-given supervision between them.",
    "For more statistical analysis, we also observed which tokens show high attention scores for 12 chosen properties, using 1000 randomly sampled molecules' cross-attention map.",
    "The result showed that tokens frequently related to certain property tend to show high attention score to that property; 'TPSA' got high attention scores towards tokens with polar atoms like oxygen and halogen atoms, 'NumHAcceptors' got tokens that involve with hydrogen bonding, and 'NumAromaticRings' got the components of aromatic rings.",
    "More detailed lists of tokens for each property can be found in Supplementary Table 2."
  ],
